{"tid":459656,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［捐血吧］腦退化患者輸年輕血漿 可望治病","createTime":"2017-11-06T02:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T04:59:14.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cbade552765b63ba9373b80edceaddcef7b609bd","tid":459656,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T02:49:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20171106/s00060/85c2128903d6427824837a287b11499d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20171106%2Fs00060%2F85c2128903d6427824837a287b11499d.jpg&h=59b5d223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】醫學專家上周六在波士頓的「阿爾茨海默氏症臨牀試驗」醫學會議上報告，稱定期把年輕捐贈者的血漿輸入患者體內，可能有助記憶與思維能力。研究員聲稱，該方法安全而沒有嚴重副作用。<br />\n<br />\n血漿是血液的液體成分，主要成分是水，亦包括溶解的血漿蛋白、葡萄糖等物質，其主要功能是運載血細胞和體內的代謝廢物。過往的老鼠研究發現，定期輸入年輕鼠的血漿有助改善年老實驗鼠的記憶力。<br />\n<br />\n改善記憶思維能力<br />\n<br />\n最新的研究由史丹福大學贊助，旨在探究上述方法是否可行安全和有助治療屬腦退化疾病的阿爾茲海默氏症。研究團隊以18名輕度至中度阿爾茲海默氏症患者為自願實驗對象，分為兩組分別被輸入生理鹽水安慰劑，以及18至30歲年輕人的血漿。經過6星期停頓期後，兩組人再對調注入體內的物質。研究員其後測試各人的記憶和思維能力，並評估其日常活動能力。<br />\n<br />\n「英國阿爾茲海默氏症研究」的研究主管勞特利奇（Carol Routledge）稱，上述研究顯示病人有改善迹象，不過仍需更多實驗對象才可確定療效。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20171106/s00014/1509905414377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171106%2Fs00014%2F1509905414377&d=PvPIn4BCo7xNqJ%2FbUytAs2xr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=7fd0f99d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171106%2Fs00014%2F1509905414377&h=6131df9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20171106/s00014/1509905414377</a>"},{"pid":"cc90d56d91547b4009b5f9a6b29b2ef0da97cbff","tid":459656,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T02:50:40.000Z","msg":"英國研究"},{"pid":"d31f4968f17cde7ed0719773b63238a8e5f3ee90","tid":459656,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T02:50:44.000Z","msg":"「英國<del>阿爾茲海默氏症</del>研究」"},{"pid":"2c9f7ea1e0b5118930b24cf28d09d9dac58985bc","tid":459656,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:19:44.000Z","msg":"捐多啲捐多啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5523da386a810f62376cae4d658d24454801fd6","tid":459656,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:29:03.000Z","msg":"等你班廢老仲日日屌人廢青wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3939fd1f35f0af0bcedcf69251074fe72446d12a","tid":459656,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:34:26.000Z","msg":"諗起silicon valley入面個有錢佬定期有後生大隻仔輸血俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a37d0258e9835145b5796ee6d78af07f4b88e3","tid":459656,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T04:00:33.000Z","msg":"（中醫角度）一滴精等於3滴血  射精俾佢得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3440e86eefba42a3fa3ea7afaeac14d3f706673f","tid":459656,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T04:02:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>（中醫角度）一滴精等於3滴血  射精俾佢得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以,找個腦退化患者給你試"},{"pid":"e67051f629151f06ae135f8e268836fed7914b07","tid":459656,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T04:48:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>（中醫角度）一滴精等於3滴血  射精俾佢得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫廢老含撚吞精<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac75427e55e8e0610814bd24248741b858eee2a4","tid":459656,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T04:51:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>（中醫角度）一滴精等於3滴血  射精俾佢得唔得<img src=\"/assets/fa